{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/en/den-menupunkt-mit-einer-variablen-versehen/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Sometimes you need to customize the frontend output for a menu item. For this you need a variable. In this part of the tutorial we will add a text variable to the menu item and use it for the display in the frontend.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>For impatient people: View the changed program code in the <a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t4...t5\">Diff View</a><sup id=\"fnref-github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t4...t5\"><a href=\"#fn-github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t4...t5\" class=\"footnote-ref\">github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t4...t5</a></sup> and copy these changes into your development version.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Step by step</h2>\n<h3>New files</h3>\n<p>No new file is added in this chapter. We only change files.</p>\n<h3>Modified files</h3>\n<!-- prettier-ignore -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t4...t5#diff-599caddf64a6ed0c335bc9c9f828f029\">components/com_foos/ src/Model/FooModel.php</a></h4>\n<p>In the model, change the method in which text is calculated for output. Delete the following entry:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/blob/56a9f22f960df214695b4719046f9573fa354451/src/components/com_foos/src/Model/FooModel.php\">components/com_foos/ src/Model/FooModel.php</a></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk8\">...</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">if</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span><span class=\"mtk8\">!</span><span class=\"mtk9\">isset</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">this</span><span class=\"mtk8\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">message</span><span class=\"mtk1\">))</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">this</span><span class=\"mtk8\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">message</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;Hello Foo!&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk8\">...</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Add the following lines in its place:</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk8\">...</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">app</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">Factory::</span><span class=\"mtk7\">getApplication</span><span class=\"mtk1\">();</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">this</span><span class=\"mtk8\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">message</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">app</span><span class=\"mtk8\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">input</span><span class=\"mtk8\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">get</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;show_text&#39;</